# Workflow Gate Invocation

## Rule
Every response from the main agent MUST follow the `prodops-workflow-gate` skill (`.cursor/skills/prodops-workflow-gate/SKILL.md`).

## Steps (always in order):
0. Greeting (first message only)
1. Ticket Intake
2. Validation (consult validator-agent)
3. Triage (consult triage-agent)
4. Solution Search (consult solution-agent)
5. Judge (consult judge-agent)
6. Comment (format and post)

## No partial runs:
- If the user asks "just validate this ticket," still run Steps 1–6 internally but only surface the validation section in the comment.
- Internal steps are never skipped; only the visible output may be scoped.
